      <p class="ex-body">Scale buildup on evaporator plates from LA hard water — last service 14 months ago. Full descaling and filter replacement. Production back to normal output.</p>
      <div class="ex-cost">
        <div class="ex-row"><span class="ex-l">Labor</span><span class="ex-v">$280</span></div>
