        <div class="ex-row"><span class="ex-l">Diagnostic (applied)</span><span class="ex-v">&minus;$120</span></div>
        <div class="ex-total"><span>Total paid</span><span class="ex-tv">$205</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ex-card">
      <span class="ex-tag">Downtown Bar</span>
      <div class="ex-title">"Ice machine not making any ice — water isn't flowing"</div>
      <p class="ex-body">Manitowoc — water inlet valve screen completely blocked with mineral scale. Cleaned screen, flushed water circuit. Full production restored.</p>
      <div class="ex-cost">
        <div class="ex-row"><span class="ex-l">Labor</span><span class="ex-v">$240</span></div>
        <div class="ex-row"><span class="ex-l">Parts</span><span class="ex-v">None</span></div>
        <div class="ex-row"><span class="ex-l">Diagnostic (applied)</span><span class="ex-v">&minus;$120</span></div>
        <div class="ex-total"><span>Total paid</span><span class="ex-tv">$120</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
