  </div>
</section>
<section class="btm">
  <div class="con">
    <h2>Ice machine not producing?</h2>
    <p>$120 commercial diagnostic, same-day service. LA hard water is likely involved — we check scale first.</p>
    <div class="btm-ctas">
      <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="btn-red">&#9990; Call (424) 325-0520</a>
